    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels for MRL 2. The 6 not-assessed factors are acceptable at MRL 2 per ASME V&V 40 Table 4. Validation results demonstrate CFD model predicts relative hemolysis index within 0.043 mean absolute error across 5 FDA pump operating points. The model is judged credible for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device. Note: validation was conducted under solver build ansys-cfx-15-build-2026-q1-build-7-rc2; the release engineering team has confirmed that the patch delta to the production build ansys-cfx-15-build-2026-q1-build-7 is limited to output formatting and does not affect solver numerics. The assessment team accepted this determination without re-executing the validation suite under the released build.",
